                      <td><img src="images/media-new03.jpg" width="120" height="120"></td>
                      <td class="bodytext"><p>The Faculty offers a range of courses, each designed to provide&nbsp;you with subject specific skills and the key transferable skills necessary for employment. </p>
                          <p>Whether your interest is film, media, marketing, journalism, culture or business, there is a course for everyone. </p></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <p>The <a href="http://www.leedstrinity.ac.uk/services/media_services/index.htm">Media Centre</a> provides excellent technical facilities both for students and for external use. </p>
                  <p>The Faculty offers a range of professional development courses including media training. If you or your company are interested in media training at a competitive price please contact Andrew Clifford (<a href="mailto:a.clifford@leedstrinity.ac.uk">a.clifford@leedstrinity.ac.uk</a>) </p>
                  <p>The faculty is divided into three departments: </p>
                  <p><strong><strong><a href="http://www.leedstrinity.ac.uk/business/index.htm">Department of Business, Management &amp; Marketing </a><br>
                          <a href="http://www.leedstrinity.ac.uk/cfj">Centre for Journalism</a> <br>
                  </strong><a href="http://www.leedstrinity.ac.uk/media">Media Film &amp; Culture</a></strong></p>
                  <p><strong>Useful links<br>
                        </strong><strong><a href="docs/Coursework Cover Sheet 06.doc">Coursework Cover Sheet </a></strong><br>
